h_{2}\left[\frac{\textrm{kJ}}{\textrm{kg}}\right]=h_{f}\left[\frac{\textrm{kJ}}{\textrm{kg}}\right]+\chi\cdot h_{fg}\left[\frac{\textrm{kJ}}{\textrm{kg}}\right]
